    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels heavy. like a long flight that never lands. i look at these landmarks and i just see things that are already dead or crumbling. there's no reason to keep traveling when the road just leads back to the same emptiness. it feels like i've already reached the end, i'm just waiting for the plane to finally touch down.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
